      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0005",
      "text": "The Fibre Channel Link Services (FC-LS) standard describes in detail the Fibre Channel Link Servic-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        539.97,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0006",
      "text": "es introduced in FC-FS-2. In addition, this document describes any ancillary functions and services",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        539.98,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0007",
      "text": "required to support the Fibre Channel Link Services.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        327.06,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0008",
      "text": "This standard was developed by the INCITS Fibre Channel T11 Technical Committee (FC-TC) of Ac-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.97,
        540.08,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0009",
      "text": "credited Standards Committee INCITS during 2003-200x. The standards approval process started in",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.97,
        539.99,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0010",
      "text": "200x. This document includes annexes which are informative and are not considered part of the stan-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.97,
        540.09,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0011",
      "text": "dard.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        118.74,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0012",
      "text": "Requests for interpretation, suggestions for improvements or addenda, or defect reports are wel-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        540.05,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0013",
      "text": "come. They should be sent to the INCITS Secretariat, Information Technology Industry Council, 1250",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        539.97,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0014",
      "text": "Eye Street, NW, Suite 200, Washington, DC 20005-3922.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        349.87,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0015",
      "text": "This standard was processed and approved for submittal to ANSI by the International Committee for",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        539.97,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p006_s0016",
      "text": "Information Technology Standards (INCITS). Committee approval of the standard does not neces-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        540.01,
        274.08
